  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare cost effectiveness of a polyurethane dressing or a vacuum therapy dressing versus
      the conventional gauze in the prevention of superficial wound infection y major cardiac
      surgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      It is a clinical prospective and randomized study. patientes will be randomized to three
      groups on the day of surgery: conventional gauze, polyurethane or vacuum therapy dressing.
      Clinical al microbiological data will be monitorized to evaluate the infection rate of
      surgical wound , mediastinitis, days of hospital stay and consumption of antimicrobials.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
